### localStorage API Usage

**Saving Data:**
```javascript
const dataToSave = {
  tasks,
  schedule,
  achievements,
  rewards,
  socialPlatforms,
  points
};
localStorage.setItem('productivityData', JSON.stringify(dataToSave));
```

**Loading Data:**
```javascript
const savedData = localStorage.getItem('productivityData');
