### Schedule Functions

#### addSchedule()
**Purpose**: Add a scheduled time block

**Code**:
```javascript
const addSchedule = () => {
  if (newSchedule.trim() && newScheduleTime) {
    const scheduleItem = {
      id: Date.now(),
      title: newSchedule,
      time: newScheduleTime,
      completed: false,
      date: new Date().toLocaleDateString()
    };
    setSchedule([...schedule, scheduleItem]);
    setNewSchedule('');
    setNewScheduleTime('');
  }
};
```

**Validation**: Title and time both required

#### toggleSchedule(id)
**Purpose**: Mark schedule item complete

```javascript
const toggleSchedule = (id) => {
  setSchedule(schedule.map(item =>
    item.id === id ? { ...item, completed: !item.completed } : item
  ));
};
```

#### deleteSchedule(id)
**Purpose**: Remove scheduled item

```javascript
const deleteSchedule = (id) => {
  setSchedule(schedule.filter(item => item.id !== id));
};
```

