### Social Media Functions

#### addSocialPost()
**Purpose**: Create post across selected platforms

**Code**:
```javascript
const addSocialPost = () => {
  if (newSocialPost.trim() && selectedPlatforms.length > 0) {
    const post = {
      id: Date.now(),
      content: newSocialPost,
      createdAt: new Date().toLocaleString(),
      engagement: 0,
      scheduled: false
    };

    setSocialPlatforms(socialPlatforms.map(platform => {
      if (selectedPlatforms.includes(platform.id)) {
        return {
          ...platform,
          posts: [post, ...platform.posts]
        };
      }
      return platform;
    }));

    setNewSocialPost('');
    setSelectedPlatforms([]);
    setPoints(points + 5);
  }
};
```

**Side Effects**:
- Adds post to each selected platform
- Awards 5 points
- Clears inputs

#### togglePlatformSelect(platformId)
**Purpose**: Toggle platform selection

```javascript
const togglePlatformSelect = (platformId) => {
  setSelectedPlatforms(prev =>
    prev.includes(platformId)
      ? prev.filter(id => id !== platformId)
      : [...prev, platformId]
  );
};
```

#### deleteSocialPost(platformId, postId)
**Purpose**: Remove specific post from platform

```javascript
const deleteSocialPost = (platformId, postId) => {
  setSocialPlatforms(socialPlatforms.map(platform =>
    platform.id === platformId
      ? { ...platform, posts: platform.posts.filter(p => p.id !== postId) }
      : platform
  ));
};
```

