### Achievement & Reward Functions

#### checkAchievements(currentPoints)
**Purpose**: Check and unlock achievements based on progress

**Code**:
```javascript
const checkAchievements = (currentPoints) => {
  const newAchievements = [];
  
  if (currentPoints >= 50 && !achievements.find(a => a.id === 'first50')) {
    newAchievements.push({ 
      id: 'first50', 
      title: '🌟 First Steps', 
      description: 'Earned 50 points', 
      unlocked: true 
    });
  }
  // ... more achievements
  
  if (newAchievements.length > 0) {
    setAchievements([...achievements, ...newAchievements]);
  }
};
```

**Conditions**:
- 50 points: First Steps
- 100 points: Century Club
- 5 tasks completed: Task Master
- 10 tasks completed: Productivity Pro

#### redeemReward(pointsNeeded, rewardName)
**Purpose**: Redeem points for reward

```javascript
const redeemReward = (pointsNeeded, rewardName) => {
  if (points >= pointsNeeded) {
    setPoints(points - pointsNeeded);
    setRewards([
      {
        id: Date.now(),
        name: rewardName,
        redeemedAt: new Date().toLocaleDateString(),
        pointsSpent: pointsNeeded
      },
      ...rewards
    ]);
  }
};
```

**Parameters**:
- `pointsNeeded`: Points required (number)
- `rewardName`: Name of reward (string)

