## 📊 State Management

### useEffect Hooks

**Data Persistence (Load)**:
```javascript
useEffect(() => {
  const savedData = localStorage.getItem('productivityData');
  if (savedData) {
    // Load all state from localStorage
  }
}, []);
```
Runs once on component mount

**Data Persistence (Save)**:
```javascript
useEffect(() => {
  const dataToSave = { tasks, schedule, ... };
  localStorage.setItem('productivityData', JSON.stringify(dataToSave));
}, [tasks, schedule, achievements, rewards, socialPlatforms, points]);
```
Runs whenever any tracked state changes

### State Dependencies

```
tasks → calculateCompletedTasks()
schedule → calculateCompletedSchedule()
socialPlatforms → calculateTotalPosts()
achievements/points → saved to localStorage
```

