### Adding Task Due Dates with Reminders

```javascript
const checkDueTasks = () => {
  tasks.forEach(task => {
    const dueDate = new Date(task.dueDate);
    const today = new Date();
    const daysUntilDue = Math.ceil((dueDate - today) / (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24));
    
    if (daysUntilDue === 1 && !task.completed) {
      console.log(`Reminder: ${task.title} is due tomorrow!`);
    }
  });
};
```

